<h2>What it does</h2>

<p>
  gabi.ru is a career intelligence platform that automates the most tedious parts of a professional job search. It continuously crawls job boards and career platforms across multiple countries, matches opportunities against your professional profile, and gives you a curated shortlist of roles worth pursuing &mdash; along with the tools to apply effectively.
</p>

<hr />

<h2>Core capabilities</h2>

<div class="feature-block">
  <div class="feature-label">Discovery</div>
  <h4>Multi-platform job crawling</h4>
  <p>
    Scans dozens of career platforms simultaneously &mdash; LinkedIn, regional job boards, government portals, international organizations, and niche industry sites. Instead of checking six different websites every morning, gabi.ru does it for you and surfaces only what matters.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="feature-block">
  <div class="feature-label">Matching</div>
  <h4>Profile-aware opportunity ranking</h4>
  <p>
    Every listing is scored against your skills, experience, career goals, and location preferences. The system understands the difference between a lateral move and a step up, and flags roles where your background is a strong fit &mdash; including positions you might not have searched for yourself.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="feature-block">
  <div class="feature-label">Application</div>
  <h4>CV and cover letter management</h4>
  <p>
    Maintains multiple versions of your CV tailored for different career paths &mdash; one for AI engineering roles, another for solutions architecture, another for leadership positions. Generates targeted cover letters for specific openings, so each application speaks directly to what the employer is looking for.
  </p>
</div>

<hr />

<h2>How it works</h2>

<p>
  You define your professional profile once &mdash; your experience, skills, target roles, preferred locations, and salary expectations. gabi.ru then:
</p>

<ol>
  <li><strong>Crawls continuously:</strong> Monitors career platforms on a schedule, picking up new listings as they appear.</li>
  <li><strong>Filters and ranks:</strong> Eliminates noise and surfaces opportunities ranked by relevance to your profile.</li>
  <li><strong>Prepares materials:</strong> For roles you want to pursue, generates or selects the right CV version and drafts a tailored cover letter.</li>
  <li><strong>Tracks progress:</strong> Keeps a record of what you applied to, when, and with which materials &mdash; so nothing falls through the cracks.</li>
</ol>

<hr />

<h2>Built for</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Professionals conducting an active, multi-market job search</li>
  <li>International candidates targeting roles across countries and languages</li>
  <li>Senior professionals who need different CV angles for different types of roles</li>
  <li>Anyone tired of manually scanning the same five job boards every day</li>
</ul>

